ISLAMABAD, Nov 17 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib on Wednesday expressed deep grief and sorrow over the death of Sheikh Rafiq Qamar, elder brother of  Federal Interior Minister Sheikh Rashid Ahmed.
In a condolence message, Farrukh Habib said death of Sheikh Rashid’s brother was a great shock.He prayed for the rest of the departed soul in eternal peace and grant of courage to the bereaved family to bear this loss with fortitude.
